{
  "stem": "21731.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] evening, I think it was-- or was it early morning-- there was a big what the German called Grossangriff.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That means a heavy bombardment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It-- all the time it was bombarded, but that was a heavy bombardment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And our barracks just went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were under the-- just-- the barracks were not very-- they were no-- they were just wood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Good that they didn't throw bombs which were fire bombs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But they were just destroyed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we climbed out from under the, the wood and whatever there was, helped others out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there was chaos, completely chaos, because the factory was also bombed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And people are running to and fro, and shouting, and crying, and giving, giving orders.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And, you know, I don't know whether you know the German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But anyway, they liked giving orders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I didn't take to these orders very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And so I told Jan, off we go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we walked off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- I had the documents in a little bag on, on me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had the documents always with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if I was told where I am-- who I am, I could show them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told Jan, we are going to Austria, not Vienna, but somewhere in the country.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, well, I think Jan explained it to me where that is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had-- I must have an idea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, we went south.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went south.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have no idea what state Germany was in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was quite extraordinary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My feelings-- because I waited for the terrible-- those Grossangriffe, I waited for them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But naturally, I knew that I can be killed and Jan can be killed also.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
